          output: "The commoners of the district gather around the foundry to witness
            the destruction as if it were a communal bonfire. The cracking of the
            timber almost manages to drown out the screams of those trapped within\u2026
            almost. Our own men cannot help but feel that we should have intervened.\r\n[Lost
            5 Bliss]"
